data.description:
One-of-a-kind estate situated on 3.65 acres of land, this remarkable 5-bedroom, 5-bathroom residence offers luxury at every turn. 

Exquisite craftsmanship and attention to detail that defines this home. The open-concept layout seamlessly flows from the formal living and dining areas into the kitchen, equipped with top-of-the-line appliances, custom cabinetry, and a center island. 

This exceptional property features a finished basement that is sure to impress, boasting a spacious room with a very large L-shaped bar, perfect for entertaining guests in style. The primary bathroom has split or dual closets, providing ample storage space, and a spa-like experience with dual shower heads for a luxurious showering experience as well as an oversized jetted tub. 

The basement is designed for ultimate relaxation and entertainment, featuring a generously sized room that rivals a primary bedroom and bathroom. Additionally, the basement offers an entertainment room where you can unwind and enjoy movie nights or game days with friends and family.

Convenience is key with two laundry rooms, one on the main level and another in the basement, ensuring effortless chores and efficient living. Imagine the ease of managing laundry tasks with multiple laundry stations at your disposal.

Set in a rural neighborhood, this property offers the perfect balance of peaceful country living and modern amenities. This property offers a gas firepit under a pergola in the backyard as well as a gated area. The sprawling acreage provides endless possibilities for outdoor activities or future expansion. Garage is heated and has a fan. 

With a blend of luxury upgrades and thoughtful design elements, this home presents a rare opportunity to experience elevated living at its finest. Don't miss your chance to own this exceptional property and create a sophisticated sanctuary that exceeds expectations. Schedule your exclusive showing today and step into a world of luxury country living.
